받아온다.</li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Git/resolve-git-conflict","tagSlugs":["/tag/git-conflict/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-04","description":"git conflict 해결하기","tags":["git_conflict"],"title":"git conflict 해결하기","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Git/resolve-git-conflict"}}}